Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位勇者真是辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.81,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚召开宴会尽情享乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀不愧是勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我们国家也就安泰了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是有报酬我才不来这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这次死伤的才几个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的多亏了勇者大人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.21,0:00:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我面对巨大的怪物毫不退缩带着骑士团的骄傲勇敢地·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.13,0:00:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到枪之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有中意的女性吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康大人累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.14,0:01:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.31,0:01:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.49,0:01:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您饿不饿东西很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想吃就吃个痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人也一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人员传送吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能更快注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人也来一口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.32,0:01:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了和你同行的拉芙塔莉雅是奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.73,0:04:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅是我的奴隶那又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.57,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了人不应该奴役别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底这个国家应该没有废除奴隶制度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是勇者勇者不能使用奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的理论吧我不这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.88,0:04:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我赢了就解放拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我赢了你打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.09,0:04:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候你就像之前一样随意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让奴隶做同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕落到底了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到你们的交谈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.99,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为勇者居然奴役亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者果然是罪人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗我同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.96,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要我是自己愿意跟着尚文大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被下了袒护主人的诅咒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.77,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心只要元康阁下获胜马上帮你解除诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.07,0:05:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.99,0:05:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗的话大不了没收你的奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会打算逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我获胜就会把拉芙塔莉雅还给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者要怎么获胜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.97,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始进行枪之勇者与盾之勇者的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.64,0:06:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将对方逼到绝境或令对方认输者胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.58,0:06:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外这场决斗将在梅洛马格国王及教皇大人的见证下进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃公正的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康大人加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.56,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个最锋利的矛和最坚固的盾谁更厉害的故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文干脆地认输吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.83,0:07:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.71,0:07:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡住了吗不愧是盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是最锋利的矛和最坚固的盾比试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没能贯穿我的盾时你已经输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾的攻击怎么可能奏效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气球怪?为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正嬴不了我就想恶心恶心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我堂堂正正地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶还挺疼卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文占了优势呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区盾之勇者居然这么对待枪之勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把神圣的决斗当成什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别继续出丑了吃香男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁谁要认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻击你的脸和两腿中间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我是卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法吗那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪电枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.28,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一决斗中有人插手刚才的结果无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伴插手决斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚张声势啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.88,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对那边的人也看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人麦茵用了魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以倒下是因为那个女人的魔法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧应该看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.98,0:11:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必相信罪人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪之勇者啊你获胜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.92,0:11:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人我明白您的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜又要独自战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千得漂亮元康阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.39,0:11:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的女儿麦帮所选择的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来知道麦茵是公主时我还吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想为世界和平作出贡献
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊一切都是他们的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了巴结自己看中的勇者让我背上冤案的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.09,0:12:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有为了女儿随意扭曲事实的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗也是一开始就设计好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.85,0:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者强行将那个女孩变成了奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定要救救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.98,0:12:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就那么想贬低我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.32,0:12:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不想来这个世界是你们把我召唤来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我遭到这样的对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.96,0:12:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者奴役的奴隶被枪之勇者漂亮地解放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就不应该召唤什么盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有盾以外的三勇者足够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种罪犯直接处置掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家不需要盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该直接把盾处死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是盾吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.99,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.62,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来解开女孩的诅咒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.72,0:13:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来你就自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激元康大人的慈悲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此这种世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我毁灭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么你对元康大人干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候求你救过我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.47,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但但是拉芙塔莉雅你被他压榨得很惨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂尚文大人什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人不会让我做不愿意做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.31,0:15:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会在我害怕、不愿意的时候用诅咒命令我战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗是不能勉强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.36,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人无法使用武器那不就只有让别人来战斗了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必去战斗只会被他使唤得浑身是伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人保护我了累了就会让我休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不尚文不是这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.55,0:15:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会对一个患病、随时可能死的奴隶伸出援手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人会给我吃我想要的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把贵重的药分给受病痛折磨的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.53,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你身边应该有其他奴隶才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下贱的亚人一副自以为是的口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有纠纷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.54,0:16:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵小姐我想听你解释一下你的违规行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您指的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违规行为?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的决斗元康是你输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人对尚文释放了魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是风魔法所以不太容易看出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该看错了吧周围观众什么都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.65,0:16:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被国王压下去了看贵族的眼神就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.66,0:16:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到王族会亲手玷污神圣的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.18,0:17:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来干什么笑我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.76,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要背叛者你走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说那个传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.98,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说尚文大人是强迫同伴的最恶劣的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不认为尚文大人做了这种…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了仁慈的元康你获得自由了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再和我有牵扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.55,0:17:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说他让你来看我惨败的模样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做您才能相信我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信?是你背叛了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么我都是尚文大人的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人你这么说又是在打算欺骗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.59,0:18:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴你们又想给我背上莫须有的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这个世界一开始就是输家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么努力都不会被人认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪它我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这面盾保护了我好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪潮时也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.41,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您明明无法战斗却用这面盾保护了村民不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是为了保护村庄才那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此尚文大人也拯救了很多生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.72,0:19:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你也是刚开始只把你当成有用的道具…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不尚文大人拯救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对我只是在考虐自己…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.11,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这个世界上最了解尚文大人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解尚文大人的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.54,0:19:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使全世界都在责怪尚文大人我也会说不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不断告诉大家尚文大人是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我的命给我剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予我活下去的意义的人是尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.48,0:20:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是您的剑不论遇到什么苦难都会跟随您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.99,0:20:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我一直想听到的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不拉芙塔莉雅她一直都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是您的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会跟随您到天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.97,0:20:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕尚文大人今后再也不相信任何人我也会相信您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信拯救了我的尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信伟大的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我阿拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可拉芙塔莉雅是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.25,0:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的您还是把我当成小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我还小不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不动就哭还碍手碍脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.01,0:21:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请让我陪在您身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者用奴隶才奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在拉芙塔莉雅也可能是被洗脑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.55,0:21:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那样的场面还能说出这种话你可真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.85,0:22:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您很难受吧今后请让我一起分担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.08,0:22:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你做的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.93,0:22:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的不过只是把城堡厨房给的剩菜夹在面包里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拉芙塔莉雅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我还不习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.57,0:22:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果亚人在小时候提升等级肉体就会成比例地急速成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚人不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们被当成野兽和魔物的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.16,0:23:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些剩菜还挺好吃的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.72,0:23:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.43,0:23:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有味道好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.98,0:23:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后一起品尝许多美味的食物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.69,0:23:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.53,0:23:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.92,0:23:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,菲洛
